   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[To the sitologoi of the village of Karanis, greeting]. I, Petheus, son of Chelloos(?), (of the cultivators) of the 60th cleruchy, [have received from you as loan of seed grain] for the present 23rd year from the grain of the past 22nd year, for 3 arourai of crown land in Karanis, 3 artabai of wheat. (2nd hand) I, Apollonios, the son of Ar- - -, have written for him [because he is illiterate]. (1st hand) Year 23, Tybi 5. (3rd hand) I, Kastor, agoranomos, have signed for three artabai.</ab>
         </div>
